title: Rogue - Philippines - May 2014
description:
True PDF | 176 Pages | English | 46,59 MB


Balancing image and intellect, Rogue tells stories with energy, insight, style, and humor. It aims to maintain a strong literary tradition by featuring thoughtful essays, sharp prose, revealing profiles, and in-depth investigative articles written by the finest writers, and accompanied by the country's top visual artists.
